      "verdict": "fabricated",
      "evidence": "logalyzer/aggregate.py:by_status() simply iterates entries and increments `c[e.status] += 1`. There is no special handling for 3xx status codes, no deduplication logic, and no double-counting. Each entry is counted exactly once by its status code."
    },
